{"tid":2089954,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人其實對香港呢個地方冇身分認同感","createTime":"2020-07-02T02:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T04:45:42.000Z","uid":205736,"like":7,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9f2bca672a98f66b625f3c5a46eaff93159c4dad","tid":2089954,"uid":205736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T02:07:52.000Z","msg":"老實講我真係好想睇香港人死<br />\n我係有小小輕度弱智<br />\n平常出去已經比人睇唔起了 <br />\n上連登又一班大學生成日笑鳩我呢d低學歷既人<br />\n香港人階級意識又明顯 <br />\n比較人工比較大學又比較中學讀邊間名校<br />\n根本網絡世界就係呢班香港人內心深處既具體化<br />\n一班鍾意睇人唔起既種族到底有咩值得留戀？"},{"pid":"d46fcf9f16a71c14f037e42e97b5430de31ae8dd","tid":2089954,"uid":60434,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T02:08:30.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身就係個垃圾地方，只係唔鍾意比外來人搞啫"},{"pid":"4bf296e48e63e259bc071ea5bfdae48a6962fc50","tid":2089954,"uid":205736,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d46fcf9f16a71c14f037e42e97b5430de31ae8dd","tid":2089954,"uid":60434,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T02:08:30.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身就係個垃圾地方，只係唔鍾意比外來人搞啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T02:10:44.000Z","msg":"既得利益者係黃絲都算<br />\n你班社會低層都做黃絲有咩用<br />\n就算比你獨立你既身分地位會有咩改變<br />\n或者係有人希望靠變黃出位黎自我實現既..."},{"pid":"2e2fe40d66abbc2492767fae4ff3f9ea723371fd","tid":2089954,"uid":205736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b6aeece6b918a76ad6e3c6b6e4c82a59834f8c","tid":2089954,"uid":34457,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T03:34:24.000Z","msg":"起底&gt;上一頁"},{"pid":"7474ac0312883a28ce82e28189c7845094fe834f","tid":2089954,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"我係有小小輕度弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as